trans-unit.source: Consists of a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> objects to be used with catalogs of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Consiste em uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> a serem usados com catálogos de controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" />.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> class is created by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in their implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> classe é criada pelas várias <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controles em suas implementações do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: For each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is created.
trans-unit.target: Para cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controle que está contido em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controle, um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objeto é criado.

trans-unit.source: This object maintains basic information about a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, including its ID, its title, its description, and a path to an associated icon.
trans-unit.target: Esse objeto mantém as informações básicas sobre um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controle, incluindo sua ID, título, sua descrição e um caminho para um ícone associado.

trans-unit.source: The various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to display a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's information in the catalog, without having to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control itself.
trans-unit.target: As várias <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controles podem usar um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objeto para exibir um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> informações do controle no catálogo, sem a necessidade de criar uma instância do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> próprio controle.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> class is used internally by the Web Parts control set to maintain a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects used in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> classe é usada internamente pelo controle Web Parts definido para manter uma coleção de todos os <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objetos usados em um catálogo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> collection is used only when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> coleção é usada somente quando uma página está no modo de exibição de catálogo.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is being rendered, it loops through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> collection, adding the information from each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to the displayed catalog.
trans-unit.target: Quando um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controle está sendo processado, percorre o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> coleção, adicionar as informações de cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objeto no catálogo exibido.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância vazia da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: This overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor can be used to create an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Esta sobrecarga do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> construtor pode ser usado para criar uma coleção vazia.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control creates an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> object if the content of an imported description file is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> controle cria vazio <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> objeto se o conteúdo de um arquivo de descrição importado é `null`.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> objects that correspond to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> controls in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> que correspondem aos controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> em um catálogo.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> object by passing in an <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância de um objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection" /> passando uma coleção <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29> constructor is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method implementations within the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to create a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29> construtor é usado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> implementações de método em vários <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controles para criar uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objetos.
